sources.title: La Poliziotta Fa Carriera 1976
sources.description: A curious woman is enlisted as a police woman thanks to her looks that impressed a police commissioner who's her neighbor. She spreads havoc since the entry exams and during the first cases she's assigned to, but ends up with a promotion. More Edwige Fenech and Alvaro Vitali comedy. They made a bunch of movies together and Alvaro made more with many of the late 70s early 80s starlets.Â  Italian with English Subtitles
